                </a>
                <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/ISO_8601" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
                    <img src="/blinkies/buttons/iso8601.png" alt="ISO 8601 YYYY-MM-DD" />
                </a>
                <img src="/blinkies/buttons/css-is-awesome.png" alt="CSS is awesome" />
